            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Rehber provides general health information and helps you find the right specialty."
          }
        },
        "tr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Rehber genel saГ„ВҹlГ„Вұk bilgisi saГ„Вҹlar ve doГ„Вҹru uzmanlГ„ВұГ„ВҹГ„Вұ bulmanГ„Вұza yardГ„ВұmcГ„Вұ olur."
